The paper deals with the problem of domain adaptation in machine learning, specifically in the context of image classification. This falls under the broad category of "Machine Learning" (cs.LG). The paper also involves the use of deep neural networks (cs.CV, cs.DL), and addresses the challenges of noisy labels (cs.AI, cs.CL). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, and cs.DL.
